headline: SolidCAD Announces Acquisition by Symetri, Part of Addnode Group
summary: SolidCAD, a leading Canadian provider and consultant of technology solutions for the architecture, engineering, construction, and manufacturing sectors, is excited to announce that it has been acquired by Symetri, a global leader in digital solutions for industries that design, build and manufacture. SolidCAD has operated in Canada as a subsidiary within the Cansel Group of Companies. This transaction marks Symetri's entry into the Canadian market.
